OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain will become more extensive
OL,7,Fthrough this evening and overnight,
OL,8,Freaching all parts. The rain mostly
OL,9,Flight but with some heavier bursts
OL,10,Fpossible. Winds still breezy at times
OL,11,Fbut remaining mild.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FOutbreaks of mostly light rain
OL,14,Fslowly easing, with drier intervals
OL,15,Fdeveloping into the afternoon.
OL,16,FHowever, a further band of heavier
OL,17,Frain will return to the northwest into
OL,18,Fthe evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
