OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,FSaturday morning, gradually turning
OL,7,Fbrighter later. Winds strengthening
OL,8,FSunday, but otherwise similar with
OL,9,Fmorning rain easing to drier
OL,10,Fconditions. Breezy Monday, but drier
OL,11,Fwith some bright spells. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
